      "name": "dark-modern",
      "description": "AI-extracted template from reference design",
      "html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Design Conversion</title>\n    <link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com\">\n    <link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://fonts.gstatic.com\" crossorigin>\n    <style>\n        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600;700&display=swap');\n\n        :root {\n            --bg: #111111;\n            --text: #FFFFFF;\n            --text-muted: #AAAAAA;\n            --subheadline-color: #00E099; /* Bright green for \"WHAT IT ACTUALLY DOES\" */\n            --surface: #1A1A1A; /* Card background */\n            --card-border-1: #00E099; /* Green for first card */\n            --card-border-2: #9747FF; /* Purple for second card */\n            --card-border-3: #CDDC39; /* Lime green for third card */\n            --active-dot-1: #00E099;\n            --active-dot-2: #9747FF;\n            --active-dot-3: #CDDC39;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            width: 1080px;\n            height: 1080px;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            background: var(--bg);\n            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;\n            color: var(--text);\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n        }\n\n        .slide {\n            width: 1080px;\n            height: 1080px;\n            padding: 60px 72px;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: space-between; /* Distribute content and footer */\n            position: relative;\n            /* Background pattern - subtle dots */\n            background-image: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,255,255,0.03) 1px, transparent 1px);\n            background-size: 80px 80px; /* Adjust for dot density */\n            background-repeat: repeat;\n        }\n\n        /* Faint lines for background pattern (top-right V-shape) */\n        .slide::before,\n        .slide::after {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            width: 1px;\n            height: 100px; /* Length of the line segment */\n            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);\n            pointer-events: none;\n            z-index: -1;\n        }\n\n        .slide::before {\n            top: 100px;\n            right: 150px;\n            transform: rotate(45deg);\n            transform-origin: top right;\n        }\n\n        .slide::after {\n            top: 100px;\n            right: 150px;\n            transform: rotate(-45deg);\n            transform-origin: top right;\n        }\n\n        .top-section {\n            margin-top: 80px; /* Adjust to push content down from top edge */\n            margin-bottom: auto; /* Push cards to bottom */\n        }\n\n        .subheadline {\n            font-size: 14px;\n            font-weight: 600;\n            text-transform: uppercase;\n            color: var(--subheadline-color);\n            margin-bottom: 16px;\n            letter-spacing: 0.1em;\n        }\n\n        .headline {\n            font-size: 72px;\n            font-weight: 700;\n            line-height: 1.1;\n            margin-bottom: 24px;\n        }\n\n        .headline .highlight {\n            color: var(--text-muted); /* Matches the grey in the design */\n            font-style: normal; /* The design doesn't show italic, just a different color */\n        }\n\n        .body-text {\n            font-size: 20px;\n            line-height: 1.5;\n            color: var(--text-muted);\n            max-width: 600px; /* Constrain width as in design */\n        }\n\n        .cards-section {\n            display: flex;\n            gap: 32px; /* Spacing between cards */\n            margin-bottom: 100px; /* Space above footer */\n        }\n\n        .card {\n            flex: 1;\n            background: var(--surface);\n            border-radius: 16px;\n            padding: 32px;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden; /* For the border effect */\n        }\n\n        .card::before {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            right: 0;\n            height: 6px; /* Thickness of the top border */\n            border-top-left-radius: 16px;\n            border-top-right-radius: 16px;\n        }\n\n        .card.card-1::before { background: var(--card-border-1); }\n        .card.card-2::before { background: var(--card-border-2); }\n        .card.card-3::before { background: var(--card-border-3); }\n\n        .card-icon {\n            margin-bottom: 24px;\n            width: 48px; /* Explicitly set icon size */\n            height: 48px;\n            display: flex; /* To center the Lucide icon */\n            align-items: center;\n            justify-content: center;\n        }\n        .card-icon svg {\n            stroke-width: 1.5; /* Adjust icon stroke for visual match */\n        }\n\n        .card-1 .card-icon svg { color: var(--card-border-1); }\n        .card-2 .card-icon svg { color: var(--card-border-2); }\n        .card-3 .card-icon svg { color: var(--card-border-3); }\n\n        .card-title {\n            font-size: 24px;\n            font-weight: 600;\n            line-height: 1.3;\n            margin-bottom: 12px;\n        }\n\n        .card-description {\n            font-size: 16px;\n            color: var(--text-muted);\n            line-height: 1.5;\n            margin-bottom: auto; /* Push active status to bottom */\n        }\n\n        .card-status {\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            font-size: 13px;\n            font-weight: 600;\n            text-transform: uppercase;\n            margin-top: 24px;\n            letter-spacing: 0.05em;\n        }\n\n        .card-status .dot {\n            width: 8px;\n            height: 8px;\n            border-radius: 50%;\n            margin-right: 8px;\n        }\n\n        .card-1 .card-status .dot { background: var(--active-dot-1); }\n        .card-2 .card-status .dot { background: var(--active-dot-2); }\n        .card-3 .card-status .dot { background: var(--active-dot-3); }\n\n        .footer {\n            position: absolute;\n            bottom: 40px;\n            left: 72px;\n            right: 72px;\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: space-between;\n            font-size: 13px;\n            color: var(--text-muted);\n        }\n    </style>\n    <script src=\"https://unpkg.com/lucide@latest\"></script>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"slide\">\n        <div class=\"top-section\">\n            <div class=\"subheadline\">{{subheadline}}</div>\n            <h1 class=\"headline\">\n                {{headline | replace(\"entire\", '<span class=\"highlight\">entire</span>') | safe}}\n            </h1>\n            <p class=\"body-text\">{{body}}</p>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"cards-section\">\n            <div class=\"card card-1\">\n                <div class=\"card-icon\">\n                    <i data-lucide=\"file-text\" style=\"width:48px;height:48px\"></i>\n                </div>\n                <h3 class=\"card-title\">Reads 50-page contracts</h3>\n                <p class=\"card-description\">Summarizes, flags risks, drafts responses</p>\n                <div class=\"card-status\">\n                    <span class=\"dot\"></span>\n                    <span>ACTIVE</span>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"card card-2\">\n                <div class=\"card-icon\">\n                    <i data-lucide=\"code\" style=\"width:48px;height:48px\"></i>\n                </div>\n                <h3 class=\"card-title\">Ships production code</h3>\n                <p class=\"card-description\">Writes, tests, and deploys \u2013 then monitors it</p>\n                <div class=\"card-status\">\n                    <span class=\"dot\"></span>\n                    <span>ACTIVE</span>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"card card-3\">\n                <div class=\"card-icon\">\n                    <i data-lucide=\"calendar\" style=\"width:48px;height:48px\"></i>\n                </div>\n                <h3 class=\"card-title\">Runs your calendar</h3>\n                <p class=\"card-description\">Books, reschedules, sends agendas autonomously</p>\n                <div class=\"card-status\">\n                    <span class=\"dot\"></span>\n                    <span>ACTIVE</span>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"footer\">\n            <div>\n                <span>Instagram</span><br>\n                <span>{{brand_name}}</span>\n            </div>\n            <span>{{cta_text}}</span>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    <script>\n        lucide.createIcons();\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>",
